data.description: This beautiful home was completely renovated in 2020. From the quaint front porch & tree swing, to the beautifully updated kitchen with quartz countertops & stainless steel appliances, this house is full of character, right down to the retro fridge, (included). This spacious home features a large bright living room, an open kitchen w/dining area, updated bathroom, 3 bedrooms upstairs, with the primary bedroom boasting a large walk-in closet as well as a standard closet. Downstairs has a very large bedroom, laundry room, (washer & dryer included), a renovated bathroom, family room, plus a bonus room to be used for whatever your buyers needs are. Brand new roof done in early 2023 as well as new carpet installed in the basement in 8/2023. This charming home is a MUST SEE! Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from County records. Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
